### 회원가입 (POST /accounts/register)
POST http://localhost:8080/accounts/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": "testuser",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "이름",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 로그인 (POST /accounts/login)
POST http://localhost:8080/accounts/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 모든 계정 조회 (GET /accounts/all)
GET http://localhost:8080/accounts/all

### 아이디로 계정 조회 (GET /accounts/{ids})
GET http://localhost:8080/accounts/testuser

### 회원 정보 수정 (PUT /accounts/{id})
PUT http://localhost:8080/accounts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": "testuser2",
  "password": "newpassword123",
  "name": "삼",
  "email": "newemail@example.com"
}

### 회원 상태 변경 (PUT /accounts/{id}/status)
PUT http://localhost:8080/accounts/1/status?status=INACTIVE

### 회원 삭제 (DELETE /accounts/{id})
DELETE http://localhost:8080/accounts/1
